===========

Bugs are tracked on `GitHub Issues <https://github.com/OCA/report-print-send/issues>`_.

`feedback <https://github.com/OCA/report-print-send/issues/new?body=module:%20server_env_printing_server%0Aversion:%2014.0%0A%0A**Steps%20to%20reproduce**%0A-%20...%0A%0A**Current%20behavior**%0A%0A**Expected%20behavior**>`_.
